e." t>c<link rel="author" title="Morten Stenshorne" href="mailto:mstensho@chromium.org"><div>
</div><style><link>
  html {
    counter-reset: pages 10;
  }
  @page {
    margin: 4em;
    counter-increment: pages 0;

    @top-center {
      text-align: left;
      vertical-align: top;
      counter-reset: pages 2;
      counter-increment: pages;
      content: counters(pages, ".");
    }
  }
  body {
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>
The number 4 should be seen in the header and footer, on every page.
